{"tid":2038170,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術都要Be water] 同一個戰術唔可以再重用","createTime":"2020-05-27T11:42:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T14:05:13.000Z","uid":112742,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"57138e360dd1c9eb78144ccf22553efcb4b357b6","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:42:50.000Z","msg":"如果你玻璃心可以上一頁<br />\n<br />\n612成功係因為第一次用<br />\n527做唔返612個效果<br />\n係因為我地變得仲慢過班立法會廢老派同狗<br />\n少數派琴晚已經入立法會 班狗早一日已經罰緊企<br />\n而我地戰術冇變 所以注定失敗<br />\n今日立法會順利開會 暫時拉左百幾人<br />\n又唔見得國際特別大迴響 <br />\n覺得呢位巴打講得幾好<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/axsxauV\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/axsxauV</a><br />\n<br />\n建議:<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">1) 唔需要再為「如果今日都唔出來反惡法 國際會點諗？」來束縛自己</span><br />\n勢色唔啱就要即刻走 <br />\n呢一年個畫面已經夠靚 核彈儲到冇位擺 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚想再有所謂核彈出現</span></strong><br />\n國際已經知道我地對支那有咩意見<br />\n有個post話「黑警係濫捕，手足唔係送頭，係表態」<br />\n佢係濫捕，但佢拉撚左你，最後你啱又點？打爆你個頭 困你48先放你返屋企，佢就收OT錢<br />\n啱啱著返團火大家似乎唔記得最重要係 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不流血 不受傷 不被捕</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2) 同一個戰術短時間內唔可以再用</span><br />\n例如和理sing /商場活動唔可以太密<br />\n再aim同一樣野 唔好用同一個戰術 (好似今日咁)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">4) 每次行動要有Plan B</span><br />\n水炮車得3部 前線狗係得咁多<br />\n佢地喺金鐘罰企就九龍新界就分薄哂 vice versa<br />\n傳統18區開花做Plan B 分得太散 <strong> <span style=\"color: red;\">D人寧願唔出都唔會想做少數派</span></strong><br />\n建議分5區 <br />\n中西區 銅鑼灣區 油尖旺區 九龍塘區  沙田區<br />\n以上地方唔會離平時開花既地區好遠 (大西北係有D遠) <br />\n而且每次最多人都係呢幾個地方<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">5) 個人認為快閃係最高cp值  班狗來到人已走 </span><br />\n快閃先會提醒到自己目標唔係要打狗 做完野就即走<br />\n<br />\n要捉你唔到就要變得快過敵人<br />\n冇必勝既戰術 思想都要Be water<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/11/28/214032_fbcbffd89a6172b9aa21bdc31a71a73f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F11%2F28%2F214032_fbcbffd89a6172b9aa21bdc31a71a73f.jpg&h=998f19fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sUFXY3o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsUFXY3o.jpg&h=91406bd7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d7fb3fdd5158a973821e0a8feb24bf07c252af06","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"旺角手足完美示範be water<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037936\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037936</a>"},{"pid":"199f327164612eb0cf2524b8ed92f3e6cd97557a","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"屌原來skip左 3) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ef7336b61bffab0bd3306231af303b14166af2","tid":2038170,"uid":86769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:47:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"be0d651bd7dce165f128280be86a24c2eb08383e","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:58:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c87e50b32ac5583a175e30149f346123d1dc4af7","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:14:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f3462c767c72a05774bdd812289bfd7df86779b","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T12:20:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c7169a43ba276b33770cdb2153465e1259f7618","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d7fb3fdd5158a973821e0a8feb24bf07c252af06","tid":2038170,"uid":112742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T11:44:35.000Z","msg":"旺角手足完美示範be water<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037936\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037936</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T13:11:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b945eb5643f50cb6ff3f33b16d163c0182495ee3","tid":2038170,"uid":115988,"like":0,"d